keter.description:
phase one is called Hochma;
phase two is called Bina; phase three [containing six Sefirot HGT
NHY] is called Zeir Anpin; and phase four is Malchut.

partzufim-of-atzilut.description:
The first is the Behinot Shorashim to the Mochin;
the second is the Behinot Mochin themselves; the third is Behinat
ZON that receive the Mochin.
